    <h1>MedReminder Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 2025</p>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>MedReminder is built by Qoreon Labs with privacy as our core principle. We believe your health data is yours alone.</p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p><strong>We collect ZERO data.</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>No personal information</li>
        <li>No health data</li>
        <li>No usage analytics</li>
        <li>No tracking</li>
        <li>No accounts required</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All your medication information is stored locally on your device using iOS secure storage. Your data:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Never leaves your device</li>
        <li>Is not backed up to our servers</li>
        <li>Is not shared with third parties</li>
        <li>Is deleted when you uninstall the app</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Notifications</h2>
    <p>MedReminder uses iOS local notifications to remind you about medications. These notifications:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Are processed entirely on your device</li>
        <li>Do not send data to external servers</li>
        <li>Require your permission to display</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>MedReminder does not integrate with any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

    <h2>iCloud Sync (Optional)</h2>
    <p>If you enable iCloud backup on your device, iOS may back up MedReminder data to your personal iCloud account. This is:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Controlled by iOS, not MedReminder</li>
        <li>Encrypted by Apple</li>
        <li>Accessible only to you</li>
        <li>Can be disabled in iOS Settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>MedReminder does not knowingly collect data from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

    <h2>GDPR Compliance</h2>
    <p>As we collect no personal data, GDPR data protection regulations are inherently satisfied. You have complete control over your data as it never leaves your device.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>If we update this privacy policy, we will notify users through the app and update the "Last Updated" date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Questions about privacy?</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@qoreonslabs.com">privacy@qoreonslabs.com</a></p>
    <p>Website: <a href="https://qoreonslabs.com">qoreonslabs.com</a></p>

    <hr style="margin: 40px 0;">
    
