---

### **Step 2: Update App Store Connect**

When submitting to App Store:

1. **App Privacy section:**
   - Select "No, we do not collect data from this app"
   - Answer all privacy questions as "No"

2. **Privacy Policy URL:**
```
   https://qoreonslabs.com/medreminder/privacy
```

3. **Support URL:**
```
   https://qoreonslabs.com/medreminder/support
